{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require broadcasters to provide subtitles & audio description of all programmes",
        "additional_details": "Audio and visual disabilities keep being overlooked and accessibility is key to ensuring generations do not get left behind in our technologically driven society. Those with disabilities should not be discriminated against, as per the protected characteristic stated in the Equality Act 2010.",
        "background": "Implement legislation to require TV broadcasters apply subtitles and audio description for live and on demand programmes, whether watched on TV, streamed, or casted to another device. ",
